text: Anaespogonius fulvus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gressitt in 1938. It is known from China.BioLib.cz - Anaespogonius fulvus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1938
title: Anaespogonius fulvus
